DATE FUNCTION

1. Find months between
2. Find system date
3. Find the total number of months or Add months
4. Find the last date


QUERIES:

SELECT MONTHS_BETWEEN('31-MAY-2024','31-JAN-2024')
FROM DUAL;
SELECT SYSDATE FROM DUAL;
